Anglo, 45% Owner of De Beers, ‘Believes in Diamonds,’ Cynthia Carroll Says

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-09-16T10:50:30Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-16/anglo-45-owner-of-de-beers-believes-in-diamonds-cynthia-carroll-says.html
Anglo American Plc (AAL) , which owns 45
percent of  De Beers , “believes in diamonds,” Chief Executive
Officer  Cynthia Carroll  said today when asked about the future
of Anglo’s shareholding in the diamond producer.  Carroll commented near Gaborone in  Botswana  today, where De
Beers announced a 10-year sales agreement with the southern
African nation.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carli Lourens in Johannesburg at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Alastair Reed at 
 areed12@bloomberg.net  